WEBVTT

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:00.552
i prijetili su nam

00:03:00.552 --> 00:03:02.860
štrajkom glađu

00:03:02.860 --> 00:03:05.158
ako se usudimo to ponuditi

00:03:05.158 --> 00:03:06.584
kao rješenje,

00:03:06.584 --> 00:03:09.655
jer nisu mogli te male stanove

00:03:09.655 --> 00:03:11.109
proširiti.

00:03:11.109 --> 00:03:13.798
Dakle zaključak s obiteljima --

00:03:13.798 --> 00:03:15.676
i to je važno,
ne naš zaključak --

00:03:15.676 --> 00:03:18.207
s obiteljima, je da imamo problem.

00:03:18.207 --> 00:03:19.945
Morali smo inovirati.

00:03:19.945 --> 00:03:22.611
Što smo učinili?

00:03:23.720 --> 00:03:27.619
Dakle, obitelj srednje klase

00:03:27.619 --> 00:03:30.499
živi razumno dobro